Participants are expected to gain insights into DOST programs and services that can assist them in advancing their business ventures.</p> <p>Topics to be discussed:</p> <ol> <li>Understanding the DOST Small Enterprise Technology Upgrading Program (SETUP)</li> <li>Maximizing Productivity in the Manufacturing Sector</li> <li>Integrating Sustainability and Resilience into a Business Continuity Plan</li> </ol>

Pariñas </b><br> Sector Head, Electronics, ICT, and Creative Industry (DOST-PCIEERD) </p> <p><b>2) Engr. Jayson B.
